│    Key Parameters:                                               │
│    - SERVO<N>_FUNCTION: Channel assignment                       │
│    - SERVO<N>_MIN: 1000 (minimum PWM)                            │
│    - SERVO<N>_MAX: 2000 (maximum PWM)                            │
│    - SERVO<N>_TRIM: 1500 (neutral PWM)                           │
