│    - Looks up channel mapping in <control channel="N">           │
│    - Applies PWM → angle conversion formula                      │
│    - Publishes angle to Gazebo topic                             │
│                                                                  │
│    PWM → Angle Formula:                                          │
│    angle = (pwm - 1500) / 500 * multiplier + offset             │
│                                                                  │
