│    - PWM 1500 → angle = 0.0 - 0.5 = -0.5                         │
│    - PWM 2000 → angle = 1.571 - 0.5 = 1.071 (clamped)           │
└────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                 │
                 │ Gazebo Topic (gz.transport)
